{"tid":2075991,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jennie眼妝被指抄襲　英美妝師直接標註YG與造型師：不是第一次！","createTime":"2020-06-23T07:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T08:35:57.000Z","uid":33359,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c56f05ac1a7f031d6d48f5746fa5a420cc87f799","tid":2075991,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"南韓女團BLACKPINK睽違1年即將於6月26日發行先行曲《How You Like That》回歸樂壇，從13日起每日都發出回歸照片與影片預熱，讓歌迷興奮不已。不過其中Jennie一個眼睛上彩繪眼妝的造型，卻被英國美妝師發現抄襲她，並直接點名YG與YG彩妝師，「從沒問過我或註明我，這是不對的！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbxpvcX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtbxpvcX.jpg&h=0ccce2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK在20日釋出的預告中，一張Jennie臉部特寫照，在左眼上的眼妝立刻引起注意，亮粉色眼妝以類似火焰的圖案框住了下眼窩，火焰延伸到了眼尾，搭配同款指甲彩繪，妝容破格十分有魅力。<br />\n<br />\n不過Jennie眼妝卻被一名叫做Nushafarin的美妝師質疑抄襲她的作品，根據她在自己經營的7萬人追蹤IG「nush.mu」上的介紹，她可能是一位阿富汗裔、在英國生活的小型美妝師。據她所稱，BLACKPINK Jennie的回歸眼妝，是她於今年2月就已經公布過的創作。<br />\n<br />\n她發表長文表示，「我對於別人因為我的作品而受到啟發、甚至二創都沒有問題，但當然要註明來源。事實上若是別人因為我而湧現靈感，是非常令人受寵若驚的。但是像YG這種大品牌花錢讓藝術家去重製我的作品，卻從來沒有通知我或是註明出處，這是不能接受的。」<br />\n<br />\n她甚至直言，「這是不對的，而且他們過去在內容創作上就發生過類似的狀況了。」批評YG已經不是第一次。她強調抄襲是違法且錯誤的行為，也試著與YG以及他們的彩妝師聯繫但都毫無回應，乾脆直接在IG上標註YG公司與彩妝師帳號，希望獲得回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1743680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1743680&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=55bac12f\" target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1743680</a>"},{"pid":"4a184ca3d4cfada4266655a4dabdd70da916f045","tid":2075991,"uid":299794,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:52:30.000Z","msg":"抄襲師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593a3dd2d984719c38cbd97a00e633975976e544","tid":2075991,"uid":555,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"化妝都有專利?"},{"pid":"ee7f0b4fe1192c95c7a19712f1cb9c162f5adc53","tid":2075991,"uid":177813,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:54:19.000Z","msg":"YG是真的仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d743e65865b2f4ac0d01fd6cc42f81ec8e7659fc","tid":2075991,"uid":106633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"印仔=返工蛇王師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28820f2299fb2a61bd7b335e42943ea944965424","tid":2075991,"uid":60256,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"抄完都冇珍妮咁正"},{"pid":"c401fbf5a5448bd005274036f71cdd91b2805427","tid":2075991,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:04:18.000Z","msg":"老闆竟然唔係開<del>gay</del>中性美idol post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f76635e0c22d136c0b518c66fcc2657f31de8be","tid":2075991,"uid":3405,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:09:26.000Z","msg":"成班blind入去𨳒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0cf1d3d0989816d249d408b51c2be328d6c919","tid":2075991,"uid":165368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 她強調這個眼妝的獨特取決於位置，放在眼睛的下方，且只有一眼，在內外眼眶都以線條輕輕勾勒，她的靈感其實是源自「刀」而非火焰<br />\n </blockquote><br />\n我地就係用火焰concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都歡迎on9ce吠番幾聲先"},{"pid":"8f3e4bec875e0bf73016421bd7c21d2797055255","tid":2075991,"uid":316329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"買左版權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ae2c933beedf414840b5cbd9197f63cc4ceb11","tid":2075991,"uid":54579,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:17:38.000Z","msg":"Jennie 最可愛, 屌你老母屈鳩人抄你， 厚唇西"},{"pid":"7ecd4dd4152f1dacb5264963b6a30645450e24c3","tid":2075991,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{